descriptionHtml:
Skyrim Save File

Created Dec 06 2011

From start completing only main quest-line. 
[spoiler]Saved after defeating Alduin.

Avoided other quests, mobs, chests, etc. to give player as \"fresh\" shot at world after as possible. 

A few misc quest activated from bumping into various random encounters.

Purchased and fully decorated Breezehome in Whiterun. Items collected during run in bedroom chest.

Be sure to check out all those Shouts granted from completing the main quest.[/spoiler]

Enjoy.
